https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/a9EMdR6xz4pxYmJ4nfCzB0zeIzq.jpg Accident on Hill Road is a cunning and energetic thriller that takes its premise from the real-life incident of a woman who hit a man, then drove home and parked the car in the garage with the man wedged halfway through her windshield. Celina Jaitly stars as Sonam Chopra, a hard-partying, overworked nursing assistant in this delicious, darkly humorous psychological thriller. Accident On Hill Road
